be disturbed in case we had sex.

01:56.020 --> 01:59.019
There's no way anyone is
walking through that door...

01:59.020 --> 02:00.499
Hello, Douglas.

02:00.500 --> 02:02.859
Victoria!

02:02.860 --> 02:06.859
But I thought you were dead!

02:10.220 --> 02:14.219
