divorced her, is that possible?

04:11.980 --> 04:14.539
Well, as I said, I'm not a lawyer, so...

04:14.540 --> 04:18.539
Yes, but you're a relationship
manager, and this is a relationship!

04:19.660 --> 04:21.259
Well, erm...

04:21.260 --> 04:22.699
