patient, Female Spock, and you know that!

12:24.820 --> 12:26.739
I think we've seen enough.

12:26.740 --> 12:29.179
Your Honour, I object!

12:29.180 --> 12:33.179
There's a brilliant bit coming up.

12:33.740 --> 12:37.739
Mr. Reynholm, are you ready to start
your cross-examination of Mrs. Reynholm?

12:38.180 --> 12:41.299
