12:43.580 --> 12:47.579
I am not in any way cross.

12:48.860 --> 12:52.099
You are Victoria Reynholm, are you not?

12:52.100 --> 12:54.499
Mr. Reynholm, we have
already established that.

12:54.500 --> 12:57.739
Might I suggest that you try less
to do an impression of a lawyer

12:57.740 --> 13:01.739
