your case as simply as you possibly can.

13:03.220 --> 13:07.179
Wise words, my learned lud.

13:07.180 --> 13:11.179
Victoria, you've spoken
about the real me,

13:11.300 --> 13:15.259
and I think it's time we heard
a little about the real you.

13:15.260 --> 13:16.939
Isn't it true, that you...

13:16.940 --> 13:20.939
Used to be a man?

13:22.340 --> 13:23.699
No.

13:23.700 --> 13:25.419
It isn't true, you say?

13:25.420 --> 13:27.139
It is untrue.

13:27.140 --> 13:31.139
Who am I thinking of?

13:31.540 --> 13:35.539
I think you mean April, the
woman you had a fight with.

13:38.580 --> 13:40.859
No further questions, my lud.

13:40.860 --> 13:43.939
What? Your entire case rested on that?

13:43.940 --> 13:45.619
Yes, your Honour.

13:45.620 --> 13:47.419
Yes, your Honour. No, wait, Mr
Reynholm, you can't leave it at that.

13:47.420 --> 13:51.419
Your Honour, may I confer with my
relationship manager? What's up, Jen?

13:52.100 --> 13:55.739
You've got to request more time
to prepare a proper defence.

13:55.740 --> 13:58.739
Your Grace, may I approach the bench?

13:58.740 --> 14:00.379
Have you brushed your teeth?

14:00.380 --> 14:01.179
No.

14:01.180 --> 14:03.659
No. Then you may not.

14:03.660 --> 14:05.939
Your Grace,

14:05.940 --> 14:09.099
I need to prepare a proper defence.

14:09.100 --> 14:13.099
The one I just did there was rubbish.

14:14.540 --> 14:17.979
Yes, he's some piece of work.

14:17.980 --> 14:21.299
We're all very happy
at Reynholm Industries.

14:21.300 --> 14:23.539
Are you telling the truth?

14:23.540 --> 14:24.819
Yes.

14:24.820 --> 14:27.059
Then why are you
so ill-at-ease?

14:27.060 --> 14:29.299
Well...

14:29.300 --> 14:32.659
If you must know... I was in
a court myself very recently...

14:32.660 --> 14:35.099
This very courtroom in fact,

14:35.100 --> 14:39.099
where I gave testimony
against a former soldier who...

14:40.580 --> 14:44.579
