Squids are already damp!

15:53.500 --> 15:56.179
Hence the phrase!

15:56.180 --> 15:57.459
Your Honour! Please!

15:57.460 --> 15:59.019
It is "squib".

15:59.020 --> 16:02.419
I must say, I find it extraordinary
that you, a man in your early 30s,

16:02.420 --> 16:06.419
could have reached this point in your
life without knowing that it is "squib".

16:08.820 --> 16:10.059
I think it's "squid".

16:10.060 --> 16:11.619
I have no further questions.

16:11.620 --> 16:12.739
No, no, no, wait, wait, wait!

16:12.740 --> 16:13.459
That will be all.

16:13.460 --> 16:14.739
Everyone has a blind spot!

16:14.740 --> 16:18.739
I said that will be all!

16:21.540 --> 16:25.219
Your name is Maurice Moss, is it not?

